Class dc1394.dc1394camera_t

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.javacpp.dc1394.dc1394camera_t
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Enclosing class:
    dc1394

    public static class dc1394.dc1394camera_t
extends org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
    Camera structure This structure represents the camera in libdc1394. It contains a number of useful static information, such as model/vendor names, a few capabilities, some ROM offsets, a unique identifier, etc...
